de them information about the issues that will be voted on during the annual meeting including decisions such as electing directors ratifying the selection of auditors and other shareholderrelated decisions including shareholderinitiated initiatives also proxies must disclose specific detailed information regarding the pay practices for certain executives       privacy policy terms of use about us contact us  salarycom all rights reserved us salaries canadian salaries purchase a salary report salaries by category salaries by income salaries by industry popular salaries negotiation tips benefits calculator search job openings job openings by state job openings by category education by career education by level education by major cost of living calculator paul b toms jr  executive bio compensation history and contacts  equilar atlas   log in  sign up x   as featured in paul b toms jr chairman and chief executive officer at hooker furniture corporation view full profile are you paul b toms jr claim your profile   sign up for equilar atlas and view paul b toms jrs full profile with equilar atlas you can identify corporate executives in paul b toms jrs network and community follow changes in paul b toms jrs employment and moneyinmotion connect with paul b toms jr through your network of contacts paul b toms jrs executive work history current chairman and chief executive officer hooker furniture corporation past to view paul b toms jrs complete executive work history sign up now age      paul b toms jrs biography paul b toms jr  has been a director since  mr toms has been chairman and chief executive officer since december  and also served as president from november  until august  mr toms was president and chief operating officer from december  to december  executive vice presidentmarketing from  to december  senior vice presidentsales  marketing from  to  and vice presidentsales from  to  mr toms joined the company in  his long tenure with the company in senior and execu