mately  million sale price includes about  million in cash and about  million in newlyissued hooker stock the release stated“although hooker furniture corp has been debtfree for some time we look at this acquisition as an excellent way to put excess capital to work and use our pristine balance sheet to layer in a manageable amount of lowcost debt” toms said in the releaseit is anticipated that hmi will operate autonomously – with the same management team – as a division of hooker which with the acquisition is expected to surpass the halfbilliondollar sales mark the release stated “we are particularly impressed with the depth and experience of the hmi management team and excited about having this level of talent join us as we plan for the future” toms saidthe companies had combined revenues of more than  million during the  months that ended oct  and total operating income for the two companies for the period was  million according to the release“while there will be no merger of operations or change in customerfacing services” toms said in the release “we do see opportunity to improve each company by sharing best practices and looking for ways to work together to lower costs improve efficiency and grow sales” toms said“the hmi team is excited to join with hooker furniture corp to become one of the largest players in the furniture industry” said hmi chief executive officer george revington “the success of these two companies is directly related to how they serve their customers and the new combination will make us even more effective and provides a great platform for future growth”following the sale revington will report to toms the release statedhooker’s purchase of hmi is expected to be finalized between feb  and march  the release indicated it noted that hooker shareholders do not have to approve the salewhen the sale is completed in addition to the bedford and hickory upholstery plants the combined company will have showrooms in high point and ho chi minh city vietnam as well as eight distribution centers in virginia north carolina california china and vietnam tags hooker furniture corp company paul b toms jr hmi furniture product line operating income most popular a day before her death likens filed a protective order against reynolds more than  indictments handed down in henry county police arrest suspect in martinsville murder case martinsville police arrest suspect in monday hit and run likens katherine white upcoming events jul  tops va  martinsville mon jul     pm jul  joshua place tue jul     pm jul  martinsville alanon group tue jul     pm jul  game on activities for adults wed jul     am jul  bible study wed jul     am findit rives s brown real estate  e church st martinsville va   bh digital marketing services  broad st martinsville va   mcville sheds  sheds direct of danville  virginia ave collinsville va   currently open svp southern virginia properties  bridge st n martinsville va   the martinsville bulletin  broad st martinsville va   find a local business special sections summer activities guide martinsville bulletin martinsville va   bh media group inc  terms of use